Package org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulators.entities

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AchievementData
    Represents data containing a list of Achievements granted and the ability to grant or remove Achievements.
    AgeableData
    Represents data that defines the owner as having a growing age process.
    AgentData
    Data regarding the toggle of AI tasks on an entity.
    AggressiveData
    Represents a toggle for an entity being "aggressive" and resorting to attacking other nearby entities if possible.
    AngerableData
    Represents a decaying "aggressive" level for entities that may attack nearby entities if provoked.
    ArtData
    Represents data pertaining to a held Art.
    BanData
    Represents a list of known Bans usually applicable to Users.
    BodyPartRotationalData
    Represents the mapped rotational data for all known body parts.
    BreathingData
    Represents the remaining air information for various entities while they are underwater.
    BreedableData
    Signifies that an entity is ready to breed.
    CareerData
    Represents the Career for a Villager.
    ChargedData
    Signifies that an entity is "charged".
    CriticalHitData
    Signifies that an entity's next attack is considered a "critical" hit.
    DamageableData
    Represents the various information for a damageable Entity such that it is aware of the previous attacker, the last amount of damage it took, etc.
    DamagingData
    Signifies that an owner is going to deal a certain amount of damage on the next "attack".
    ElderData
    Signifies that an entity is considered an "elder".
    ExperienceHolderData
    Represents the "gained" experience information.
    ExpirableData
    Signifies that an entity will expire after the value has decayed to the minimum.
    ExplosiveRadiusData
    Represents the "explosion radius" of an Explosive entity.
    EyeLocationData
    Represents the "eye" location of an Entity.
    FallingBlockData
    Represents the information for a FallingBlock.
    FlamableData
    Signifies that an Entity is on fire, but does not have a set expiration for being aflame.
    FlyingData
    Signifies that an Entity is "flying".
    FoodData
    Represents the food information for Humans.
    FuseData
    Represents the "fuse" for a FusedExplosive.
    GameModeData
    Represents the GameMode of a Player.
    GriefingData
    Signifies that an Entity can "grief" blocks in a world.
    HealingSourceData
    Signifies that an Entity is "healing" the owning DataHolder.
    HealthData
    Represents the health information for a Living entity.
    HorseData
    Represents Horse information specific to HorseStyle, HorseColor, and HorseVariant.
    IgniteableData
    Signifies that an Entity is on fire for a remaining duration of "ticks".
    InvisibilityData
    Signifies that an Entity is rendered "invisible" to viewing Players.
    InvulnerabilityData
    Signifies that an Entity is "invulnerable" to any sort of damage for an expiring period of "tick"s.
    JoinData
    Represents the original join Date that a User or Player originally joined a server with.
    KnockbackData
    Signifies that an Entity will "knock back" on the next attack.
    LeashData
    Signifies that an Entity is currently "leashed" to the Entity leash holder.
    OcelotData
    Represents the OcelotType for an Ocelot.
    OrbData  
    PassengerData
    Signifies that an Entity is a "passenger" of another Entity.
    PersistingData
    Signifies that an Entity will "persist" across restarts of the game.
    PlayerCreatedData
    Signifies that an Entity was originally created by a Player.
    PlayingData
    Signifies that a Villager is "playing".
    RabbitData
    Represents the RabbitType of a Rabbit.
    RespawnLocationData
    Represents the location of which a data holder may respawn at.
    SaddleData
    Signifies that a Entity is currently "saddled".
    ScreamingData
    Signifies that an entity is currently "screaming".
    ShatteringData
    Signifies that an entity will "shatter" upon expiration.
    ShearedData
    Signifies that an entity is currently "sheared" and will regrow at some point.
    SittingData
    Signifies that an Entity is currently "sitting".
    SizeData
    Represents the base and height sizes of an entity if it has physical form.
    SkeletonData
    Represents the SkeletonType of a Skeleton.
    SleepingData
    Signifies that the owner is currently "sleeping".
    SlimeData
    Represents the size of a Slime.
    SneakingData
    Signifies that an entity is currently "sneaking".
    StatisticData
    Represents the container of all known applied Statistics and Achievements.
    TameableData
    Signifies that an entity is "tamed" and has an owner.
    TargetLivingData
    Represents the current targets of an owner that is "targeting" some Living entities.
    TradeOfferData
    Represents a list of TradeOffers that a Merchant may use.
    VehicleData
    Signifies that an entity is currently being ridden by another Entity.
    VelocityData
    Represents the current velocity of an entity.
    VillagerZombieData
    Signifies that a Zombie is a "villager" zombie.
    WhitelistData
    Signifies that a Player or User is "whitelisted" on the server.
